### Get user by ID
# Replace this GUID with a real one from the create response
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/b93d94b8-c186-45a7-bbd2-6517608b6642
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete user by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/b93d94b8-c186-45a7-bbd2-6517608b6642
Accept: application/json